answers.body_markdown:
Without more information, we can only guess.  Assuming that you have a `List&lt;Process&gt;` where each `Process instance` contains `three ints`. You could do it like this.  Here, a record is used as the Process class.
```
record Process(int getCpu, int getSomethingElse1, int getSemeThingElse2) {}
List&lt;Process&gt; processes = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(); // populated with Process info
Collections.sort(processes, Comparator.comparingInt(Process::getCpu));

