Found a solution finally. 
I didnt notice at the begining but the `&lt;div&gt;` was inside of an iframe. 
The code below solved the problem. 

    driver.switchTo().frame(&quot;frameName&quot;);
    WebElement emailAddyField = driver.findElement(By.id(&quot;email&quot;));
    emailAddyField.sendKeys(username);
    driver.switchTo().defaultContent();

